# Audit engagement (feature 001-erp-staged-audit)
# Artefact directories and phase-report JSON are committed for traceability.
# Raw evidence (log dumps, CSV extracts, PII-adjacent outputs), tenant-id maps,
# and the isolated audit venv are NOT committed — they must be recreated
# per-run against the current staging snapshot and deterministic seed.
.venv-audit/
docs/audit/evidence/
docs/audit/synthetic-data-seed/tenant-ids.yaml
docs/audit/dep-inventory/
docs/audit/baseline/perf-baseline.md
docs/audit/backlog.xlsx
